12:33.669 --> 12:34.754
calls turn to hand holding,

12:34.837 --> 12:36.839
hand holding turns into teen pregnancy,

12:36.922 --> 12:38.966
-unemployment, lady baldness...
-You know what,

12:39.049 --> 12:41.677
I was relying on our generation's
total disregard

12:41.761 --> 12:43.137
for basic human interaction.

12:43.721 --> 12:44.680
Are you serious?

12:46.599 --> 12:48.392
[Sierra on phone]
It's Sierra. Leave a message.

12:50.186 --> 12:52.188
[automated voice]
To keep this greeting, press one.

12:52.688 --> 12:54.690
To rerecord, press two.

12:56.358 --> 12:57.193
[phone beeps]

12:59.111 --> 13:01.739
Hey, it's 555-0147.

13:02.448 --> 13:05.117
[Sierra on phone] Hey, it's 555-0147.

13:05.367 --> 13:07.495
[automated voice]
