15:18.626 --> 15:20.002
You guys know that girl Veronica?

15:20.085 --> 15:21.670
Do we know a girl called Veronica?

15:21.754 --> 15:23.839
Remember the hottest girl
I've seen up close?

15:23.923 --> 15:26.425
-Who you won't stop yapping about.
-Do we remember that girl?

15:26.634 --> 15:29.094
Well, we made major progress last night.

15:29.511 --> 15:30.429
Oh, my God.

15:30.554 --> 15:31.805
