a smoking piece and you ain't funny.

15:46.028 --> 15:48.656
-I'm funny.
-No, you're not.

15:48.948 --> 15:50.658
That's okay, you don't have to be.

15:50.866 --> 15:52.576
You should send a pic with your shirt off.

15:53.619 --> 15:55.287
Did you tell tell her your dirty secrets?

15:55.371 --> 15:57.081
Like you're a loser
with Frodos for friends.

15:57.164 --> 15:59.708
-Federal government investment is needed--
-Right!

16:00.501 --> 16:02.503
But, AIDS now is airborne,

16:02.586 --> 16:04.964
so we all going to die,
so everything that you said

16:05.047 --> 16:06.548
is a moot point. Give it to me.

16:06.632 --> 16:09.259
-I made you flash cards.
-[scattered applause]

16:09.343 --> 16:10.177
-Boom!
-[boy] Yeah!

16:10.260 --> 16:11.303
[whistle blows]

16:11.387 --> 16:12.680
-Let's go.
-[boy mutters]

16:20.312 --> 16:21.146
Okay.

16:26.276 --> 16:28.278
[sighs]

16:28.737 --> 16:29.613
[camera shutter snaps]

16:32.324 --> 16:33.701
[mutters] No, it's stupid.

16:45.337 --> 16:46.171
[shutter snaps]

16:55.389 --> 16:56.223
[shutter snaps]

17:03.856 --> 17:04.732
[phone dings]

17:10.529 --> 17:11.363
[Sierra gasps]

17:16.076 --> 17:16.910
Frick!

17:58.327 --> 18:00.537
[quietly] Disregard that last message.

18:10.547 --> 18:11.381
[phone chimes]

18:38.534 --> 18:39.910
This really what guys want?

18:40.619 --> 18:41.453
Yeah.

18:41.870 --> 18:42.913
Well, most guys.

18:44.081 --> 18:45.457
You just figuring that out?

18:46.125 --> 18:47.918
Never really had to think about it before.

18:49.795 --> 18:50.629
[phone chimes]

19:04.309 --> 19:07.521
No, fireball, ready? Fireball.

19:07.604 --> 19:08.605
[phone chimes repeatedly]

19:10.524 --> 19:11.441
