Too easy.

1:23:14.030 --> 1:23:16.116
[girl About time
someone took her down a peg.

1:23:27.544 --> 1:23:28.378
[whistle blows]

1:23:37.929 --> 1:23:39.347
Jamey! You okay?

1:23:40.223 --> 1:23:41.057
Jamey!

1:23:41.516 --> 1:23:42.600
Call the medic!

1:23:47.605 --> 1:23:50.233
[girl] Ronnie, Ronnie,
where are you going?

1:23:53.737 --> 1:23:55.280
[boy] Felt so good!

1:23:58.116 --> 1:23:59.909
Hey, hey. Alright, alright.

1:24:00.243 --> 1:24:01.161
Here, look at me.

1:24:02.370 --> 1:24:04.748
-How many fingers am I holding up?
-Two.

1:24:05.540 --> 1:24:07.250
-Jamey!
-Sierra, wait!

1:24:08.293 --> 1:24:09.878
-Sierra?
-Sierra,

1:24:09.961 --> 1:24:12.088
why did you do this to me?
-Wait. Veronica.

1:24:12.172 --> 1:24:15.216
-Are you cheating on me with Spence?
-No!

1:24:15.300 --> 1:24:17.218
Jamey, I'm not.
And I'm not who you think I am,

1:24:17.302 --> 1:24:18.803
and she's not who you think she is.

1:24:18.887 --> 1:24:21.056
She's been pretending to be me
and I've been her,

1:24:21.139 --> 1:24:23.183
and she's been catfishing you
this entire time.

1:24:23.266 --> 1:24:25.518
No, okay, wait. Please, listen to me.

1:24:25.602 --> 1:24:28.772
-You have to let me explain, okay, please.
-Wait, your voice.

1:24:29.647 --> 1:24:32.108
-[coach] Alright, that's enough.
-Please, just give me a second.

1:24:32.192 --> 1:24:33.359
[coach] Let's get outta  here.

1:24:34.944 --> 1:24:36.738
Just stay the hell away from me.

1:24:38.907 --> 1:24:39.824
Both of you.

1:24:43.244 --> 1:24:44.746
Why did you do this to me?

1:24:45.330 --> 1:24:46.539
You kissed him.

1:24:47.123 --> 1:24:48.124
I saw you kiss him.

1:24:48.208 --> 1:24:50.877
Well, he thinks I'm you, remember?
That was the whole plan.

1:24:52.045 --> 1:24:54.255
You whine about your looks,

1:24:54.672 --> 1:24:56.883
but you've no idea what it's like
to be me.

1:24:58.927 --> 1:25:01.137
I told you things I haven't told anyone.

1:25:02.180 --> 1:25:03.306
You think I'm mean?

1:25:03.973 --> 1:25:05.433
You should check the mirror,

1:25:05.517 --> 1:25:08.019
because your looks are
the least ugly thing about you.

1:25:18.822 --> 1:25:20.532
Sierra, Sierra.

1:25:20.698 --> 1:25:22.117
Please tell me that wasn't you.

1:25:24.410 --> 1:25:25.954
Come on, you hate Veronica.

1:25:26.913 --> 1:25:28.331
Sierra, that was just wrong.

1:25:30.500 --> 1:25:32.418
I don't even know who you are anymore.

1:25:38.174 --> 1:25:39.717
Sierra, honey, what's wrong?

1:25:40.385 --> 1:25:41.594
[crying] You know, it's...

1:25:41.928 --> 1:25:45.598
it's easy for you to spout
your self-esteem BS,

1:25:46.599 --> 1:25:47.934
but look at me.

1:25:49.352 --> 1:25:54.440
Do you have any idea what it's like to be
a teenage girl and to look like this?

1:25:57.610 --> 1:26:00.196
Of course not, because you're tiny,

1:26:00.446 --> 1:26:01.990
you're tiny and you're beautiful

1:26:02.073 --> 1:26:03.867
and you've always been beautiful.

1:26:05.201 --> 1:26:07.412
And this is what you stuck me with.

1:26:55.710 --> 1:26:57.712
[plays melancholy tune]

1:27:17.023 --> 1:27:20.610
And thus concludes our unit on mitosis.

1:27:21.861 --> 1:27:23.529
We now enter telophase,

1:27:24.447 --> 1:27:26.199
during which the cell

1:27:26.491 --> 1:27:28.201
cleaves apart forever

1:27:28.785 --> 1:27:30.286
in two distinct cells.

1:27:49.055 --> 1:27:50.348
About the assignment.

1:27:50.598 --> 1:27:52.225
[Ms. T] I asked for a poem.

1:27:52.308 --> 1:27:53.685
You turned in a song.

1:27:53.768 --> 1:27:57.063
I know. I just really wanted to do
my own thing.

1:27:57.146 --> 1:27:59.607
Your own thing was also late.

1:28:03.111 --> 1:28:05.989
But it was emotional, raw...

1:28:06.531 --> 1:28:08.783
and those are the marks of a true artist.

1:28:08.866 --> 1:28:10.535
You are very special.

1:28:11.327 --> 1:28:13.579
And I hope when the time comes,

1:28:13.788 --> 1:28:16.791
you will allow me to write you
a college recommendation.

1:28:17.750 --> 1:28:18.626
Thank you.

1:28:19.419 --> 1:28:20.837
In the meantime,

1:28:20.920 --> 1:28:22.880
whoever you wrote those words for,

1:28:22.964 --> 1:28:24.841
you should tell him, or her...

1:28:26.050 --> 1:28:29.512
