1:28:30.430 --> 1:28:31.264
I will.

1:28:40.440 --> 1:28:41.274
Dad.

1:28:42.525 --> 1:28:43.735
Can we talk?

1:29:13.222 --> 1:29:14.682
I'm sorry I suck so bad.

1:29:23.483 --> 1:29:24.525
