1:36:30.743 --> 1:36:32.953
I mean, bad, like, really bad,

1:36:33.037 --> 1:36:34.246
-and...
-I know.

1:36:34.622 --> 1:36:36.040
And I'm so sorry.

1:36:38.501 --> 1:36:42.671
